Web RTC 
—————

Introduction
——————

	* Is an API definition
	* That supports applications like
		* Voice calling
		* Video calling
		* P2P File sharing
	* This API is supposed to be implemented by web browsers

Status
———

	* WebRTC is a part of an ongoing initiative by IETF group of W3C to define real time communication for web browsers.


Design
————

	* The major components of WebRTC are 

		* UserMedia - the get User
		* Peer Connection
		* Data Channel
